 = September 20, 2014 | accessdate = September 21, 2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180129195302/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3909&p=.htm | archive-date = 2018-01-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。根據電影票銷售網站[[Fandango_(公司)|Fandango]]，《移動迷宮》成為最大的賣家，佔早期門票銷售額的50％以上<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.forbes.com/sites/dorothypomerantz/2014/09/19/does-the-maze-runner-mark-the-beginning-of-the-end-of-the-ya-movie-craze/ | title = Does 'The Maze Runner' Mark The Beginning Of The End Of The YA Movie Craze? | first = Dorothy | last = Pomerantz | publisher = ''Forbes'' | date = September 19, 2014 | accessdate = September 21, 2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180311203337/https://www.forbes.com/sites/dorothypomerantz/2014/09/19/does-the-maze-runner-mark-the-beginning-of-the-end-of-the-ya-movie-craze/ | archive-date = 2018-03-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。電影於2014年9月19日在美國和加拿大橫跨3,604個地點並超過350家[[IMAX|IMAX]]影院發行<ref>{{cite news | url = https://variety.com/2014/film/news/box-office-maze-runner-will-outrace-walk-among-the-tombstones-1201307683/ | title = Box Office: 'Maze Runner' Will Outrace 'Walk Among the Tombstones' | first = Brent | last = Lang | publisher = ''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]'' | date = September 17, 2014 | accessdate = September 19, 2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180129195320/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/box-office-maze-runner-will-outrace-walk-among-the-tombstones-1201307683/ | archive-date = 2018-01-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://deadline.com/2014/09/box-office-preview-maze-runner-to-put-tombstones-in-ground-this-is-where-i-leave-you-debuts-836131/ | title = Box Office Preview: 'Maze Runner' To Put 'Tombstones' In Ground; 'This Is Where I Leave You' Debuts | first = Anita | last = Busch | publisher = Deadline.com | date = September 18, 2014 | accessdate = September 19, 2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180312083459/https://deadline.com/2014/09/box-office-preview-maze-runner-to-put-tombstones-in-ground-this-is-where-i-leave-you-debuts-836131/ | archive-date = 2018-03-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。電影從周四晚上的活動中賺得110萬美元<ref>{{cite web | url = http://deadline.com/2014/09/maze-runner-late-nights-box-office-walk-among-the-tombstones-this-is-where-i-leave-you-836376/ | title = Box Office Late Nights: 'Maze Runner' Off To Good Start With $1.1M, 'Tombstones' Takes In $480K | first = Anita | last = Busch | publisher = Deadline.com | date = September 19, 2014 | accessdate = September 19, 2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180312083524/https://deadline.com/2014/09/maze-runner-late-nights-box-office-walk-among-the-tombstones-this-is-where-i-leave-you-836376/ | archive-date = 2018-03-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，並於開畫當天賺得$1,125萬美元<ref>{{cite web | url = http://deadline.com/2014/09/maze-runner-box-office-walk-among-the-tombstones-this-is-where-i-leave-you-837209/ | title = Box Office Friday: 'Maze Runner' Over $30M; Liam's Leisurely 'Walk' To $14M; 'Where I Leave You' Stays Put At No. 3 | first = Anita | last = Busch | publisher = Deadline.com | date = September 20, 2014 | accessdate = September 20, 2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171107002815/http://deadline.com/2014/09/maze-runner-box-office-walk-among-the-tombstones-this-is-where-i-leave-you-837209/ | archive-date = 2017-11-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。它在首映周末的收益高達3,250萬美元，列為票房榜首，其中的9％是來自IMAX影院<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2014/09/21/box-office-maze-runner-races-to-32-5m-weekend/ | title = Box Office: 'Maze Runner' Races To $32.5M Weekend, Kevin Smith's 'Tusk' Bombs | first = Scott | last = Mendelson | publisher = ''Variety'' | date = September 21, 2014 | accessdate = September 21, 2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180616002622/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2014/09/21/box-office-maze-runner-races-to-32-5m-weekend/ | archive-date = 2018-06-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。其開畫周末的收益是9月份發行的電影中