=== 評價 ===
《[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]》表示，評論家們認為由於電影中的「精彩的演出和令人毛骨悚然的神秘氣氛」，使這部電影比大部分的青少年小說改編的電影來得更好<ref>{{cite news | last=Ryan | first=Tim | url=https://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/09/19/the-maze-runner-this-is-where-i-leave-you-a-walk-among-the-tombstones-tusk-review-revue/ | title='The Maze Runner,'This Is Where I Leave You,' 'Tusk': Review Revue | work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] | date=September 19, 2014 | accessdate=October 13, 2014 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702042552/https://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/09/19/the-maze-runner-this-is-where-i-leave-you-a-walk-among-the-tombstones-tusk-review-revue/ | archive-date=2018-07-02 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]網站上，根據160個評論，電影得到65％的新鮮度<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_maze_runner/ | title=The Maze Runner | work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | publisher=[[Flixster|Flixster]] | accessdate=2014-09-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613120021/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_maze_runner | archive-date=2016-06-13 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，平均得分為6/10。該網站的共識指出：「憑藉強勁的演技，堅實的前提，和令人耳目一新的黑暗方式來敘述它的反烏托邦設定，《移動迷宮》從YA科幻歷險的擁擠領域中脫穎而出<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_maze_runner/ | title=The Maze Runner | work=rottentomatoes.com | publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate=January 17, 2018 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613120021/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_maze_runner | archive-date=2016-06-13 | dead-url=no }}</ref>」。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]網站上，根據34個評論的得分為56/100，<ref>[http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-maze-runner {{Wayback|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-maze-runner |date=20151004113136 }} [[Metacritic|Metacritic]]]</ref>，表示「混合或平均的評價」<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-maze-runner | title=The Maze Runner Reviews | work=metacritic.com | publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | accessdate=October 1, 2016 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151004113136/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-maze-runner | archive-date=2015-10-04 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。《CinemaScore》的觀眾調查中，在A+至F的評級中，這齣電影得到的評級為「A-」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-maze-runner-surges-734290|title=Box Office: 'Maze Runner' Surges Friday Night for $30M-Plus Debut; 'Tombstones' Distant No. 2|accessdate=September 20, 2014|work=The Hollywood Reporter|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140920182953/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-maze-runner-surges-734290|archive-date=2014-09-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《{{link-en|新聞日|Newsday}}》的拉夫·古斯曼（Rafer Guzman）給了這部電影3/4分，並形容它為「堅實，精心製作和具娛樂性」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/movies/the-maze-runner-review-the-hunger-games-for-boys-1.9338758|title='The Maze Runner' review: 'The Hunger Games' for boys|accessdate=September 18, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180428011634/https://www.newsday.com/entertainment/movies/the-maze-runner-review-the-hunger-games-for-boys-1.9338758|archive-date=2018-04-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{link-en|RogerEbert.com|RogerEbert.com}}》的克里斯蒂·萊米爾（Christy Lemire）說她認為這部電影很耐人尋味的，她寫道：「它告訴我們一個我們認為自己以前聽過無數次的故事，但有一種令人耳目一新的不同語調與細節的程度<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-maze-runner-2014|title=THE MAZE RUNNER: Review|accessdate=September 18, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180428093653/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-maze-runner-2014|archive-date=2018-04-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。《[[西雅圖時報|西雅圖時報]]》的索倫安德森（Soren Anderson）說這部電影「遠遠優於它小說的啟發」，並給予3/4的分數<ref>{{cite web|url=http://seattletimes.com/html/entertainment/2024565097_mazerunnerxml.html?syndication=rss|title='The Maze Runner': Well-cast thriller outpaces the book|accessdate=September 18, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218184840/http://seattletimes.com/html/entertainment/2024565097_mazerunnerxml.html?syndication=rss|archive-date=2014-12-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[聖荷西信使報|聖荷西信使報]]》的托尼·希克斯（Tony Hicks）表示「迷上了優秀演技的組合，耐人尋味的前提與引人入勝的佈景」<ref name="mercurynews.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/entertainment/ci_26552668/maze-runner-perks-up-tired-ya-action-formula?source=rss|title=Review: 'The Maze Runner' perks up tired YA action formula|accessdate=September 18, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055049/http://www.mercurynews.com/entertainment/ci_26552668/maze-runner-perks-up-tired-ya-action-formula?source=rss|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[澳洲廣播公司|澳洲廣播公司]]》的馬修·圖米（Matthew Toomey）給了這部電影A−的評級，其迷人的前提予以讚揚，說它「在整整兩個小時的播映期間，它保持了他的注意力」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefilmpie.com/index.php/review/3296-review-the-maze-runner|title=Review: The Maze Runner|accessdate=September 18, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180428011626/http://www.thefilmpie.com/index.php/review/3296-review-the-maze-runner|archive-date=2018-04-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》的賈斯汀·羅威（Justin Lowe）說它是「始終如一地具吸引力<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/maze-runner/review/731801|title='The Maze Runner': Film Review|accessdate=September 18, 2014|work=The Hollywood Reporter|first=Justin|last=Lowe|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022141453/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/maze-runner/review/731801|archive-date=2015-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>」，而《{{link-en|綜藝電影評論|Variety Film Reviews}}》的{{link-en|艾拉·泰勒|Ella Taylor}}寫道：「隨著世界創作YA影片的發展，《移動迷宮》的低科技和妥善的故事情節驅動讓人感覺耳目一新<ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/film-review-the-maze-runner-1201301782/|title=Film Review: 'The Maze Runner'|accessdate=September 18, 2014|work=Variety|first=Ella|last=Taylor|date=September 10, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140914113527/http://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/film-review-the-maze-runner-1201301782/|archive-date=2014-09-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。

《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的米高·奧沙利文（Michael O'Sullivan）說：「移動迷宮揭開了一些謎團，但它旋轉得更多」，並給它3/4的評分<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/goingoutguide/movies/the-maze-runner-movie-review-theres-no-escaping-a-thrilling-cliffhanger/2014/09/18/0aaa6b78-3dda-11e4-9587-5dafd96295f0_story.html|title='The Maze Runner' movie review: There's no escaping a thrilling cliffhanger|accessdate=September 18, 2014|work=The Washington Post|first=Michael|last=Ou2019sullivan|date=September 18, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171205163359/https://www.washingtonpost.com/goingoutguide/movies/the-maze-runner-movie-review-theres-no-escaping-a-thrilling-cliffhanger/2014/09/18/0aaa6b78-3dda-11e4-9587-5dafd96295f0_story.html|archive-date=2017-12-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{link-en|紐華克明星總帳|The Star-Ledger}}》的史提芬·威提（Stephen Whitty）寫道：「它確實留下讓你想看下一輯電影的希望，而這是少有的從YA的電影拉過來的一個特殊效果<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2014/09/the_maze_runner_review_lost_in_the_ya_labyrinth.html|title='The Maze Runner' review: Escaping the YA labyrinth|accessdate=September 18, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117125428/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2014/09/the_maze_runner_review_lost_in_the_ya_labyrinth.html|archive-date=2017-11-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。」《我們有這覆蓋（We Got This Covered）》的艾薩克·費爾德伯格（Isaac Feldberg）授予該電影8/10顆星，並稱之為「黑暗、危險和不尋常的驚險」，同時讚譽它為「最吸引人的YA改編之一，在相當的一段時間裡在戲院裡上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/the-maze-runner-review/|title=The Maze Runner Review|accessdate=September 23, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171204010442/http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/the-maze-runner-review/|archive-date=2017-12-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」《{{link-en|弗雷斯諾蜜蜂|The Fresno Bee}}》的里克·本特利（Rick Bentley）稱讚導演[[韋斯·波爾|韋斯·波爾]]的執導方向，說他「在薄薄但堅實的劇本與一流的動作之間創造了平衡 — 而他並不會浪費製作的框架<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fresnobee.com/2014/09/17/4129660/action-carries-the-maze-runner.html?sp=/99/1355/209/229/1182/|title=Action carries 'The Maze Runner'|accessdate=September 18, 2014|archive-date=2014-09-18|archive-url=https://archive.today/20140918222924/http://www.fresnobee.com/2014/09/17/4129660/action-carries-the-maze-runner.html?sp=/99/1355/209/229/1182/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。」《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》的比爾·域卡（Bill Zwecker）稱它為「一部演技精湛及智能驚悚片／未來主義科幻與節奏輕快的電影<ref>{{cite news|url=http://entertainment.suntimes.com/entertainment-news/maze-runner-satisfying-sci-fi-ride/|title='THE MAZE RUNNER': A SATISFYING SCI-FI RIDE|accessdate=September 18, 2014|work=Chicago Sun-Times|date=September 18, 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140921082643/http://entertainment.suntimes.com/entertainment-news/maze-runner-satisfying-sci-fi-ride/|archivedate=2014-09-21|deadurl=yes}}</ref>」。《[[紐約_(雜誌)|紐約雜誌]]》的{{link-en|比奇·埃比裡|Bilge Ebiri}}說是「非常鉚接的<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ebiri|first1=Bilge|title=Not Knowing Anything About The Maze Runner Isn't a Bad Way to See It|url=http://www.vulture.com/2014/09/movie-review-the-maze-runner.html|accessdate=September 27, 2014|publisher=vulture.com|date=September 18, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180321070237/http://www.vulture.com/2014/09/movie-review-the-maze-runner.html|archive-date=2018-03-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>」。《{{link-en|奧蘭治縣登記報|Orange County Register}}》的{{link-en|米高·斯雷高|Michael Sragow}}給它一個B級，並說：「儘管韋斯·波爾很熟練的喚起各種幽閉恐怖症，無論在迷宮幽地的開放式監獄，或是迷宮裡的實際狹窄空間，他都能夠引發出[[狄倫·歐布萊恩|戴倫·奧拜恩]]一觸即發的表現<ref>{{cite news|last1=Sragow|first1=Michael|title='Maze Runner' captures a young-adult dystopia|url=http://www.ocregister.com/articles/maze-635592-glade-thomas.html|accessdate=September 27, 2014|publisher=ocregister.com|date=September 18, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170324001910/http://www.ocregister.com/articles/maze-635592-glade-thomas.html|archive-date=2017-03-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」

《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》的克勞迪婭·普格（Claudia Puig）說：「一齣科幻驚悚片設置在一個模糊的未來後世界末日啟示錄，它必須創建一個完全繪製了的宇宙來徹底地打動觀眾。然而感覺到《移動迷宮》只是部分形成」，故給它2/4分<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2014/09/18/the-maze-runner-review/15476845/|title='Maze Runner' puzzles, and not in a good way|accessdate=September 18, 2014|work=USA Today|date=September 18, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171127221522/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2014/09/18/the-maze-runner-review/15476845/|archive-date=2017-11-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》的{{link-en|理查德·科利斯|[Richard Corliss}}說：「就像[[尚-保羅·薩特|尚-保羅·薩特]]《沒有退出主義》一樣，但那是更擁擠，和跟瓶裝睾酮的麝香放在一起那樣」<ref>{{cite news|last1=Corliss|first1=Richard|title=Review: The Hunger Games Meets Lord of the Flies in The Maze Runner|url=http://time.com/3394382/the-maze-runner-movie-review/|accessdate=September 27, 2014|publisher=time.com|date=September 17, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201165142/http://time.com/3394382/the-maze-runner-movie-review/|archive-date=2017-12-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{link-en|格蘭特闌|Grantland}}》網站的{{link-en|衛斯理·莫里斯|Wesley Morris}}說：「我認為我感到有一點大災變的感受 — 長時間接觸系列中的三至四部作品時會造成過多的睡意，而當中受尊敬的演員代表著反對受政府壓抑的青年叛變者」<ref>{{cite news|last1=Morris|first1=Wesley|title=Small(er) Movie Roundup: Now Big Enough to Include America's YA Movie Flavor of the Week!|url=http://grantland.com/hollywood-prospectus/movie-review-maze-runner-zero-theorem-drop-skeleton-twins/|accessdate=September 27, 2014|publisher=grantland.com|date=September 24, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180418192129/http://grantland.com/hollywood-prospectus/movie-review-maze-runner-zero-theorem-drop-skeleton-twins/|archive-date=2018-04-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。《[[費城詢問報|費城詢問報]]》的{{link-en|費史提分·雷亞|Steven Rea}}在4分裡給此電影2.5分，並說：「這是個黯淡的生意，並隨著它爆破的急速發展和說明性的結論，電影也變得荒謬了<ref>{{cite news|last1=Rea|first1=Steven|title='The Maze Runner': Mixed-up, confused kids with no directions home|url=http://www.philly.com/philly/entertainment/movies/20140919__The_Maze_Runner___Mixed-up__confused_kids_with_no_directions_home.html|accessdate=September 27, 2014|publisher=philly.com|date=September 18, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006131418/http://www.philly.com/philly/entertainment/movies/20140919__The_Maze_Runner___Mixed-up__confused_kids_with_no_directions_home.html|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」《[[波士頓環球報|波士頓環球報]]》的影評人{{link-en|伊森·吉爾斯多夫|Ethan Gilsdorf}}說：「青少年應該吃掉這個幻想的場景，咀嚼焦慮與厄運，而生還與賦權成為了故事中的希望（這必然在續集裡待續）<ref>{{cite news|last1=Gilsdorf|first1=Ethan|title='The Maze Runner' comes to the screen|url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/arts/movies/2014/09/18/the-maze-runner-comes-screen/bYESg0Z1ROGgyuF9xyDHuI/story.html|accessdate=September 27, 2014|publisher=bostonglobe.com|date=September 18, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171202052459/http://www.bostonglobe.com/arts/movies/2014/09/18/the-maze-runner-comes-screen/bYESg0Z1ROGgyuF9xyDHuI/story.html|archive-date=2017-12-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」另外，有評論指故事不太完整、劇情虎頭蛇尾、且結局不太讓人滿意<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.mtime.com/2014/09/22/1531910-2.html#content |language= |title=《移动迷宫》周末北美夺冠 |publisher=时光网 |date=2014-09-22 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028175051/http://news.mtime.com/2014/09/22/1531910-2.html#content |archive-date=2014-10-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

