== 續集 ==
{{main|移動迷宮：焦土試煉|移動迷宮：死亡解藥}}
2013年10月11日，報導指[[二十世紀福克斯|二十世紀福克斯]]已購得第二部小說《[[移動迷宮：焦土試煉_(小說)|移動迷宮：焦土試煉]]》的版權。劇本繼續由{{le|T·S·諾林|T.S. Nowlin}}撰寫，而導演[[韋斯·波爾|韋斯·波爾]]共同監督劇本的工作<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://collider.com/maze-runner-sequel-movie-scorch-trials/ |title=Fox Hires Writer to Start Work on MAZE RUNNER Sequel THE SCORCH TRIALS |last=Chitwood |first=Adam |date=October 11, 2013 |publisher=Collider |accessdate=October 11, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731074256/http://collider.com/maze-runner-sequel-movie-scorch-trials/ |archive-date=2017-07-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年7月25日，波爾在[[聖地亞哥國際動漫展|聖地亞哥國際動漫展]]上宣布，他們將於2015年3月至5月開始拍攝工作，電影於影院開畫時將會獲得成功<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/maze-runner-sequel-the-scorch-trials-concept-art/ |title=The Maze Runner Sequel The Scorch Trials Concept Art Revealed [Comic Con 2014] |last=Sciretta |first=Peter |date=July 25, 2014 |publisher=slashfilm.com |accessdate=July 26, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140924041123/http://www.slashfilm.com/maze-runner-sequel-the-scorch-trials-concept-art/ |archive-date=2014-09-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，在電影發行前的兩星期，二十世紀福克斯決定繼續推進第三輯的續集，並於2014年9月初在[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]開始電影的前期製作<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.buzzfeed.com/jarettwieselman/a-maze-runner-sequel-is-already-in-pre-production?s=mobile | title = A "Maze Runner" Sequel Is Already In Pre-Production | first = Jarett | last = Wieselman | date = September 4, 2014 | accessdate = September 6, 2014 | website = Buzzfeed | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171121033913/https://www.buzzfeed.com/jarettwieselman/a-maze-runner-sequel-is-already-in-pre-production?s=mobile | archive-date = 2017-11-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。電影團隊亦是用原班人馬和新增幾個新的角色：荷西、布蘭達、詹森以及亞里斯<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/maze-runner-sequel-the-scorch-trials-concept-art/ |title=The Maze Runner Sequel The Scorch Trials Concept Art Revealed [Comic Con 2014] |last=Sciretta |first=Peter |date=2014-07-25 |publisher=slashfilm.com |accessdate=2014-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140729070841/http://www.slashfilm.com/maze-runner-sequel-the-scorch-trials-concept-art/ |archive-date=2014-07-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據悉，[[埃丹·吉倫|埃丹·吉倫]]將會加入飾演詹森（鼠人"Rat-Man"）<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/game-thrones-actor-play-villain-734722 |title='Game of Thrones' Actor to Play Villain in 'Maze Runner' Sequel (Exclusive) |last=Kit |first=Borys |date=September 26, 2014 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=September 26, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930091022/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/game-thrones-actor-play-villain-734722 |archive-date=2017-09-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[羅莎·薩拉查|羅莎·薩拉查]]飾演布蘭達<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/rosa-salazar-nabs-key-female-736918 |title=Rosa Salazar Nabs Key Female Role in 'Maze Runner' Sequel (Exclusive) |last=Kit |first=Borys |date=September 30, 2014 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=September 30, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141004021305/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/rosa-salazar-nabs-key-female-736918 |archive-date=2014-10-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[雅各布·洛夫蘭|雅各布·洛夫蘭]]飾演阿里斯·瓊斯<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/mud-actor-joins-maze-runner-737285 |title='Mud' Actor Joins 'Maze Runner' Sequel (Exclusive) |last=Kit |first=Borys |date=October 1, 2014 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=October 1, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180316153858/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/mud-actor-joins-maze-runner-737285 |archive-date=2018-03-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而[[吉安卡洛·伊坡托|吉安卡洛·伊坡托]]飾演豪爾赫·加拉拉加<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/breaking-bad-actor-joins-maze-737805 |title='Breaking Bad' Actor Joins 'Maze Runner' Sequel 'Scorch Trials' (Exclusive) |last=Kit |first=Borys |date=October 2, 2014 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=October 2, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930084546/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/breaking-bad-actor-joins-maze-737805 |archive-date=2017-09-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[移動迷宮：焦土試煉|移動迷宮：焦土試煉]]》於2015年9月9日上映<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.ettoday.net/news/20140922/404343.htm| title = 《移動迷宮2：焦土試煉》已開拍　「打鐵趁熱」明年播| author = ETtoday 新聞雲記者華少甫| date = 2014-09-23| accessdate = 2014-09-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140926080835/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20140922/404343.htm| archive-date = 2014-09-26| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

《移動迷宮系列》的第二部續集《[[移動迷宮：死亡解藥|移動迷宮：死亡解藥]]》繼續由{{le|T·S·諾林|T.S. Nowlin}}擔任編劇，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/03/the-maze-runner-the-death-cure-movie-ts-nowlin-fox-1201385970/|title=‘Maze Runner: The Death Cure’ Sets T.S. Nowlin To Pen|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|author=Anita Busch|date=2015-03-04|accessdate=2015-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150310003443/http://deadline.com/2015/03/the-maze-runner-the-death-cure-movie-ts-nowlin-fox-1201385970/|archive-date=2015-03-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年3月，導演波爾表示，若他能繼續執導的話，那第三集將不會被分拆成兩集發布<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/the-death-cure-movie/|title=‘The Maze Runner’ Finale ‘The Death Cure’ Won’t Be Split Into Two Movies|publisher=[http://www.slashfilm.com/ slashfilm.com]|author=Peter Sciretta|date=2014-10-09|accessdate=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024234129/http://www.slashfilm.com/the-death-cure-movie/|archive-date=2014-10-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年7月9日，據透露《[[移動迷宮：死亡解藥|移動迷宮：死亡解藥]]》將於2016年2月開始拍攝<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/ClevverTV/status/619370026202566656|title=The script for Death Cure is currently being worked on & will begin filming in February #ScorchTrials #ScorchSneakPeek|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|author=ClevverTV|date=2015-07-09|accessdate=2015-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220450/https://twitter.com/ClevverTV/status/619370026202566656|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然而後來延遲至2016年3月才正式開始拍攝。電影先前計劃於2017年2月17日在美國上映，但期間因為[[狄倫·歐布萊恩|戴倫·奧拜恩]]受傷的關係而延遲拍攝，使電影無法順利在原訂的日期推出。2016年5月27日二十世紀福克斯宣布，電影的上映日期更改為2018年1月26日。

